snippet.title: Meghan Markle Secret Recording Exposes Feud With Prince William And Kate Middleton
snippet.description:
Is Meghan Markle tearing the royal family apart?

Meghan Markle Duchess of Sussex has just been exposed for who she really is by a possible video, which was secretly recorded. Did you know that royal family feuds are still alive today? Watch this video and you’ll be up to date with the most recent royal drama. Its no surprise that all the drama is stirring around Meghan because that has been happening since day one. So who will win in this giant royal feud? And who moved out of the palace? Watch the video to find out. And don’t forget to subscribe to The Talko for more news on the Royal family!
